1
00:01:37,850 --> 00:01:41,000
[The Epoch of Miyu]

2
00:01:41,090 --> 00:01:44,000
[Episode 38]

3
00:01:55,229 --> 00:01:58,979
[Meeting Room]

4
00:02:01,290 --> 00:02:02,830
[Mr. Wei]

5
00:03:01,750 --> 00:03:02,630
This recording

6
00:03:02,630 --> 00:03:04,310
isn't directly related

7
00:03:04,310 --> 00:03:06,150
to the wiretapping incident,

8
00:03:06,630 --> 00:03:08,190
but we can use it

9
00:03:10,630 --> 00:03:11,590
against them.

10
00:03:12,250 --> 00:03:13,110
Exactly.

11
00:03:13,530 --> 00:03:15,530
Let's fan the flames for Wei Siyuan.

12
00:03:21,590 --> 00:03:22,320
Enjoy your meal.

13
00:03:22,320 --> 00:03:23,030
Thank you.

14
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:24,590
The environment here is nice, right?

15
00:03:24,590 --> 00:03:25,150
Yes.

16
00:03:28,750 --> 00:03:29,560
Mrs. Wei.

17
00:03:32,070 --> 00:03:33,530
Hello. Please take a seat.

18
00:03:37,010 --> 00:03:38,230
So you are Xu Miyu.

19
00:03:39,850 --> 00:03:41,250
What do you want from me?

20
00:03:45,110 --> 00:03:46,570
Please take a look at this.

21
00:03:50,920 --> 00:03:51,680
Who is this?

22
00:03:51,940 --> 00:03:53,540
This is Lu Zhenzhen's child.

23
00:04:04,650 --> 00:04:06,230
[The DNA test]

24
00:04:06,260 --> 00:04:07,900
[on the parental relationship
between Nie Quan and Wei Siyuan]

25
00:04:11,530 --> 00:04:12,720
Why are you telling me this?

26
00:04:12,720 --> 00:04:14,650
Lu Zhenzhen's husband is my ex.

27
00:04:15,810 --> 00:04:17,670
They are now divorced.

28
00:04:18,029 --> 00:04:20,470
Her next target is Mr. Wei.

29
00:04:20,500 --> 00:04:21,500
No way.

30
00:04:22,590 --> 00:04:24,000
I already made this vixen

31
00:04:24,020 --> 00:04:25,290
get out of Purong.

32
00:04:25,330 --> 00:04:27,560
Seems I was too polite to her.

33
00:04:28,200 --> 00:04:29,320
I'll find someone

34
00:04:29,340 --> 00:04:30,660
to deal with her.

35
00:04:30,690 --> 00:04:33,350
I'll make her disappear
from the Shanghai Bund.

36
00:04:33,730 --> 00:04:35,330
Mrs. Wei, don't be angry yet.

37
00:04:35,500 --> 00:04:37,250
I have something else here.

38
00:04:37,280 --> 00:04:38,480
Please have a listen.

39
00:04:39,650 --> 00:04:44,650
[Recording]

40
00:04:40,680 --> 00:04:43,030
This little guy is so good.

41
00:04:43,620 --> 00:04:44,740
My baby.

42
00:04:45,090 --> 00:04:46,760
You already have a son and a daughter.

43
00:04:46,760 --> 00:04:48,280
And your wife is so fierce.

44
00:04:48,390 --> 00:04:50,290
Will you love our baby?

45
00:04:50,500 --> 00:04:51,960
Don't worry about that bitch.

46
00:04:51,960 --> 00:04:52,760
Rest assured.

47
00:04:53,180 --> 00:04:55,130
Once Purong is acquired by Kuanli,

48
00:04:55,190 --> 00:04:57,970
I'll take the money

49
00:04:58,159 --> 00:04:59,750
and take you and the baby

50
00:04:59,840 --> 00:05:01,280
abroad

51
00:05:01,300 --> 00:05:02,250
to live a good life.

52
00:05:02,250 --> 00:05:03,040
We three will enjoy

53
00:05:03,040 --> 00:05:04,190
the family happiness

54
00:05:04,190 --> 00:05:06,760
together.

55
00:05:06,790 --> 00:05:08,790
Shameless!

56
00:05:11,720 --> 00:05:13,860
Mrs. Wei, don't be angry.

57
00:05:14,010 --> 00:05:16,130
I understand how you feel right now.

58
00:05:16,150 --> 00:05:18,880
I have experienced everything
you are going through.

59
00:05:18,880 --> 00:05:20,710
Lu Zhenzhen is despicable,

60
00:05:20,730 --> 00:05:21,870
but

61
00:05:22,060 --> 00:05:24,540
a husband's betrayal is more painful

62
00:05:24,610 --> 00:05:26,040
and unbearable.

63
00:05:26,060 --> 00:05:27,100
No wonder

64
00:05:27,260 --> 00:05:28,990
Wei is always

65
00:05:29,010 --> 00:05:30,740
badmouthing you in front of me.

66
00:05:31,190 --> 00:05:31,830
It turns out

67
00:05:31,830 --> 00:05:32,950
he and that vixen

68
00:05:32,950 --> 00:05:34,510
hooked up a long time ago.

69
00:05:35,080 --> 00:05:35,890
Xu Miyu.

70
00:05:36,960 --> 00:05:37,720
How should we

71
00:05:38,330 --> 00:05:40,450
punish this adulterous couple?

72
00:05:48,280 --> 00:05:48,930
[Purong Hotel]

73
00:05:49,980 --> 00:05:52,270
[Purong Hotel]

74
00:05:50,340 --> 00:05:51,070
Mr. Xue.

75
00:05:51,560 --> 00:05:52,159
By the way,

76
00:05:52,390 --> 00:05:54,710
I saw a package for Mr. Wei in the lobby.

77
00:05:54,750 --> 00:05:56,310
Do you want to sign for it?

78
00:05:56,990 --> 00:05:57,430
Okay.

79
00:06:00,990 --> 00:06:04,130
[Internal Office] [Convention Center]

80
00:06:13,050 --> 00:06:13,990
Yes.

81
00:06:14,170 --> 00:06:15,650
Didn't I tell you not to disturb me?

82
00:06:15,650 --> 00:06:16,330
Mr. Wei.

83
00:06:19,680 --> 00:06:20,940
I'll call you back.

84
00:06:24,750 --> 00:06:25,480
Mr. Ji.

85
00:06:27,110 --> 00:06:28,440
What a rare guest.

86
00:06:29,140 --> 00:06:30,070
Long time no see.

87
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:32,170
Where are you working lately?

88
00:06:33,610 --> 00:06:35,030
You're forgetful, Mr. Wei.

89
00:06:35,030 --> 00:06:36,470
I was fired.

90
00:06:36,500 --> 00:06:38,360
Which hotel would dare to hire me?

91
00:06:38,920 --> 00:06:40,240
Sorry, I forgot.

92
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:43,360
You're

93
00:06:43,390 --> 00:06:44,950
too impulsive.

94
00:06:45,300 --> 00:06:46,980
But it's understandable.

95
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:48,210
That's about love, huh?

96
00:06:48,210 --> 00:06:49,560
Ever since ancient times,

97
00:06:49,560 --> 00:06:51,440
men have gone mad for beauty.

98
00:06:54,680 --> 00:06:56,670
Thank you for understanding, Mr. Wei.

99
00:06:56,670 --> 00:06:57,850
But to be honest,

100
00:06:58,450 --> 00:06:59,600
I do regret it a bit.

101
00:06:59,920 --> 00:07:01,590
Regret now?

102
00:07:03,100 --> 00:07:04,260
For what?

103
00:07:07,130 --> 00:07:09,490
I regret doing something unnecessary.

104
00:07:12,040 --> 00:07:12,970
What do you mean?

105
00:07:15,270 --> 00:07:16,600
Actually, the spyware

106
00:07:16,750 --> 00:07:17,950
on Xu Miyu's phone

107
00:07:17,950 --> 00:07:19,190
was installed by you.

108
00:07:19,550 --> 00:07:21,460
The listening device in Marcos' room

109
00:07:21,460 --> 00:07:23,190
was also installed by your man.

110
00:07:23,970 --> 00:07:26,210
I suggest you stop before it's too late

111
00:07:26,700 --> 00:07:30,500
and take the initiative to tell
the facts to the investigation team.

112
00:07:30,660 --> 00:07:33,200
That way, you might still have a way out.

113
00:07:33,530 --> 00:07:36,060
Using the investigation team
to pressure me?

114
00:07:36,610 --> 00:07:37,940
Try to scare me?

115
00:07:37,970 --> 00:07:39,830
Don't shed crocodile tears here.

116
00:07:40,520 --> 00:07:42,159
The spyware on Xu Miyu's phone

117
00:07:42,159 --> 00:07:43,830
is an undeniable fact.

118
00:07:43,940 --> 00:07:44,630
The listening device

119
00:07:44,630 --> 00:07:46,890
was also planted in Marcos's room by her.

120
00:07:47,050 --> 00:07:47,840
Listen.

121
00:07:47,870 --> 00:07:49,220
Xu Miyu can't escape
the hotel's punishment

122
00:07:49,220 --> 00:07:51,220
just because the video was deleted.

123
00:07:51,280 --> 00:07:53,300
There will definitely be more evidence.

124
00:07:53,300 --> 00:07:54,530
Once I find it,

125
00:07:54,780 --> 00:07:56,340
she'll be fired.

126
00:07:57,700 --> 00:07:58,620
Well,

127
00:07:59,230 --> 00:08:01,430
I have to let you listen to the evidence.

128
00:08:02,040 --> 00:08:02,900
What evidence?

129
00:08:06,410 --> 00:08:07,410
Honey?

130
00:08:22,750 --> 00:08:23,640
Honey?

131
00:08:25,380 --> 00:08:26,070
Honey?

132
00:08:26,880 --> 00:08:28,630
Where are you going
with your things?

133
00:08:28,630 --> 00:08:30,050
I'm going to my mom's.

134
00:08:30,080 --> 00:08:32,010
Her lumbar disc is acting up again.

135
00:08:33,740 --> 00:08:34,320
Is it serious?

136
00:08:34,320 --> 00:08:36,360
Do you want me to go with you to see her?

137
00:08:36,360 --> 00:08:37,120
No, no.

138
00:08:37,400 --> 00:08:39,860
Just focus on your hotel business.

139
00:08:41,409 --> 00:08:43,620
How's that matter going on your end?

140
00:08:43,770 --> 00:08:44,690
Which one?

141
00:08:45,150 --> 00:08:46,390
What Niu Qiankun has asked you

142
00:08:46,390 --> 00:08:47,870
to help with.

143
00:08:48,070 --> 00:08:48,790
Didn't you help him

144
00:08:48,790 --> 00:08:50,320
get Liberty Group's

145
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:51,330
base price?

146
00:08:51,350 --> 00:08:52,750
Did he give you the money?

147
00:08:53,150 --> 00:08:54,390
Not yet.

148
00:08:54,870 --> 00:08:56,120
As soon as the listening device
was planted,

149
00:08:56,120 --> 00:08:58,120
it was discovered by Liberty Group.

150
00:08:58,210 --> 00:08:59,550
It caused a huge uproar.

151
00:08:59,680 --> 00:09:01,920
Since Yuntian Group
is delaying the bid award,

152
00:09:01,920 --> 00:09:03,770
Niu Qiankun refuses to pay.

153
00:09:04,020 --> 00:09:06,150
Or I would have gone with you to see Mom.

154
00:09:07,470 --> 00:09:09,790
Niu Qiankun is not keeping his word.

155
00:09:10,150 --> 00:09:11,630
Wasn't it agreed that

156
00:09:11,650 --> 00:09:14,560
your task would be regarded as finished

157
00:09:14,950 --> 00:09:16,690
after you planted the listening device
in the other party's room

158
00:09:16,690 --> 00:09:18,170
and let him know their base price?

159
00:09:18,170 --> 00:09:19,460
He wants to renege, right?

160
00:09:19,460 --> 00:09:20,520
I'll question him.

161
00:09:21,240 --> 00:09:22,620
Alright, don't be angry.

162
00:09:22,620 --> 00:09:23,390
Calm down,

163
00:09:23,390 --> 00:09:24,480
and take it easy.

164
00:09:26,560 --> 00:09:28,440
I'm partly to blame for this.

165
00:09:28,470 --> 00:09:29,890
My subordinates didn't do a good job,

166
00:09:29,890 --> 00:09:31,620
so the bid can't be awarded now.

167
00:09:31,810 --> 00:09:33,560
You know Niu Qiankun well.

168
00:09:33,680 --> 00:09:34,550
If he can't make money,

169
00:09:34,550 --> 00:09:35,790
how could he pay me?

170
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:37,380
But don't worry, Honey.

171
00:09:37,380 --> 00:09:38,930
I'm trying to find a way these two days

172
00:09:38,930 --> 00:09:40,130
to get Yuntian Group

173
00:09:40,150 --> 00:09:41,920
to award the bid as soon as possible.

174
00:09:41,920 --> 00:09:43,340
Once this is settled,

175
00:09:43,430 --> 00:09:45,420
I'll take you, our daughter and son

176
00:09:45,750 --> 00:09:47,030
to immigrate to Australia.

177
00:09:47,030 --> 00:09:48,560
We can retire and chill out,

178
00:09:48,790 --> 00:09:49,940
lying on the beach every day,

179
00:09:49,940 --> 00:09:50,550
eating barbecue,

180
00:09:50,550 --> 00:09:51,550
and drinking.

181
00:09:51,870 --> 00:09:53,130
What a wonderful life!

182
00:09:54,670 --> 00:09:57,390
That subordinate you mentioned

183
00:09:57,510 --> 00:09:59,790
is Lu Zhenzhen, that vixen, right?

184
00:10:02,630 --> 00:10:03,950
Her?

185
00:10:04,180 --> 00:10:05,790
Don't misunderstand, Honey.

186
00:10:05,790 --> 00:10:07,790
She's just a tool to me.

187
00:10:09,310 --> 00:10:10,630
You know,

188
00:10:11,170 --> 00:10:12,200
your family's

189
00:10:12,230 --> 00:10:14,050
Kaixin, Qian Xun,

190
00:10:14,080 --> 00:10:15,100
and Huang Chengmin

191
00:10:15,100 --> 00:10:16,640
were all taken away by Ji.

192
00:10:16,670 --> 00:10:18,800
I really have no one left to work for me.

193
00:10:19,630 --> 00:10:21,150
Is this woman reliable?

194
00:10:21,960 --> 00:10:24,590
They say she's very scheming.

195
00:10:27,560 --> 00:10:30,010
This woman just cares about money.

196
00:10:30,090 --> 00:10:32,890
I promised her a little money.

197
00:10:32,920 --> 00:10:35,160
She'll handle all these things.

198
00:10:35,190 --> 00:10:38,440
Even if we fail,
she'll take the blame for me.

199
00:10:38,660 --> 00:10:41,520
Isn't that killing two birds
with one stone, Honey?

200
00:10:41,950 --> 00:10:43,940
You men are all bad.

201
00:10:45,270 --> 00:10:46,880
I treat other women badly.

202
00:10:46,910 --> 00:10:48,510
Isn't that how it should be?

203
00:10:48,590 --> 00:10:51,170
I only love you.

204
00:10:51,810 --> 00:10:52,570
Honey.

205
00:11:03,510 --> 00:11:05,170
It's no use trying to snatch it.

206
00:11:05,170 --> 00:11:06,720
This is just for you to hear.

207
00:11:06,840 --> 00:11:07,830
A backup of the recording

208
00:11:07,830 --> 00:11:10,560
has already been sent
to the investigation team.

209
00:11:13,440 --> 00:11:14,640
What does this prove?

210
00:11:16,270 --> 00:11:17,480
What does this prove?

211
00:11:17,970 --> 00:11:20,510
It's just a private chat
between me and my wife at home.

212
00:11:20,510 --> 00:11:21,990
Who knows if it's true or false?

213
00:11:21,990 --> 00:11:24,110
Will the investigation team
call the police to arrest me over this?

214
00:11:24,110 --> 00:11:24,910
You're too naive.

215
00:11:24,910 --> 00:11:26,390
Whether you can be arrested or not

216
00:11:26,390 --> 00:11:27,480
is up to the police.

217
00:11:27,800 --> 00:11:28,560
Besides,

218
00:11:28,590 --> 00:11:32,520
the anonymous email connected
to the listening device has been found.

219
00:11:32,770 --> 00:11:33,570
What?

220
00:11:34,410 --> 00:11:36,010
It's right in your computer.

221
00:11:41,890 --> 00:11:42,760
Mr. Wei,

222
00:11:42,780 --> 00:11:44,580
the investigation team is here.

223
00:11:52,800 --> 00:11:53,440
Mr. Wei,

224
00:11:54,350 --> 00:11:55,880
come back with us for a chat.

225
00:11:55,970 --> 00:11:58,100
Don't believe in Ji Feng's nonsense.

226
00:11:58,310 --> 00:12:00,140
This has nothing to do with me.

227
00:12:02,060 --> 00:12:03,520
Please escort Mr. Wei out.

228
00:12:09,330 --> 00:12:11,320
What right do you have to take me away?

229
00:12:11,320 --> 00:12:14,010
I am the general manager of Purong Hotel.

230
00:12:14,910 --> 00:12:15,790
Look,

231
00:12:17,180 --> 00:12:18,490
do I have the right?

232
00:12:21,640 --> 00:12:22,580
Aunt.

233
00:12:23,240 --> 00:12:24,770
Aunt, you're finally here.

234
00:12:24,920 --> 00:12:25,920
Please save me.

235
00:12:26,450 --> 00:12:27,550
Ji Feng is framing me.

236
00:12:27,550 --> 00:12:28,360
He is setting me up.

237
00:12:28,360 --> 00:12:29,810
I didn't do anything, Aunt.

238
00:12:29,810 --> 00:12:30,870
You have to help me.

239
00:12:31,050 --> 00:12:32,910
I have already seen the evidence.

240
00:12:34,160 --> 00:12:35,280
You dare to do it,

241
00:12:35,970 --> 00:12:37,430
but don't dare to admit it?

242
00:12:39,150 --> 00:12:40,360
Aunt.

243
00:12:42,030 --> 00:12:42,750
Aunt.

244
00:12:44,010 --> 00:12:45,820
Ji Feng forced me.

245
00:12:46,550 --> 00:12:49,630
He made things difficult
for me again and again,

246
00:12:50,360 --> 00:12:51,820
so I took a desperate risk.

247
00:12:51,870 --> 00:12:52,530
Aunt,

248
00:12:52,960 --> 00:12:54,400
please save me, Aunt.

249
00:12:54,740 --> 00:12:55,750
The investigation team works for you.

250
00:12:55,750 --> 00:12:56,630
As long as you say a word,

251
00:12:56,630 --> 00:12:57,870
they won't make things difficult for me.

252
00:12:57,870 --> 00:12:59,390
I can't let them take me away.

253
00:12:59,390 --> 00:12:59,870
Aunt,

254
00:12:59,870 --> 00:13:01,240
didn't you say

255
00:13:01,270 --> 00:13:03,300
you would leave Purong Hotel to me?

256
00:13:03,500 --> 00:13:04,190
Aunt.

257
00:13:07,150 --> 00:13:08,120
I thought

258
00:13:09,460 --> 00:13:10,970
you would repent.

259
00:13:21,290 --> 00:13:22,290
Call the police.

260
00:13:24,160 --> 00:13:27,040
Let him be punished by the law.

261
00:13:28,140 --> 00:13:29,290
Aunt, don't call the police.

262
00:13:29,290 --> 00:13:29,760
Aunt,

263
00:13:29,790 --> 00:13:30,520
Aunt.

264
00:13:30,980 --> 00:13:31,680
Aunt,

265
00:13:32,330 --> 00:13:34,600
why did you choose him in the end?

266
00:13:34,620 --> 00:13:36,080
I am your family.

267
00:13:36,080 --> 00:13:36,720
Aunt.

268
00:13:37,580 --> 00:13:38,300
Aunt.

269
00:13:38,950 --> 00:13:40,430
Aunt, please forgive me.

270
00:13:40,450 --> 00:13:42,570
Give me another chance, Aunt.

271
00:13:43,040 --> 00:13:44,070
Aunt.

272
00:14:33,640 --> 00:14:34,590
Hello, Mr. Ji.

273
00:14:36,450 --> 00:14:37,730
Hello, Mr. Ji.

274
00:14:51,940 --> 00:14:52,700
Madam.

275
00:15:06,030 --> 00:15:07,360
Welcome back.

276
00:15:08,540 --> 00:15:11,420
The future of Purong Hotel
is in your hands.

277
00:15:13,700 --> 00:15:14,600
Madam.

278
00:15:14,920 --> 00:15:16,820
There are fewer than two weeks left.

279
00:15:16,820 --> 00:15:17,940
I will do my best.

280
00:15:17,970 --> 00:15:19,100
I won't let you down.

281
00:15:22,060 --> 00:15:23,060
Hello, everyone.

282
00:15:23,490 --> 00:15:25,150
I want to share some good news.

283
00:15:25,560 --> 00:15:26,610
Purong Hotel

284
00:15:26,630 --> 00:15:29,300
is getting back on track step by step.

285
00:15:29,450 --> 00:15:31,680
But if we want to improve our performance,

286
00:15:31,680 --> 00:15:34,210
we still need everyone's concerted
efforts.

287
00:15:34,240 --> 00:15:35,430
Are you confident?

288
00:15:35,460 --> 00:15:36,820
-Yes.
-Yes.

289
00:15:38,240 --> 00:15:39,550
Not loud enough.

290
00:15:39,570 --> 00:15:40,810
-Yes.
-Yes.

291
00:15:54,270 --> 00:15:56,390
No matter

292
00:15:56,410 --> 00:15:58,940
which position you rotate to in the hotel,

293
00:15:58,970 --> 00:16:00,520
remember the slogan,

294
00:16:00,540 --> 00:16:01,940
"Making guests feel at home".

295
00:16:01,940 --> 00:16:04,420
It's the service tenet of Purong Hotel.

296
00:16:04,440 --> 00:16:08,100
I hope that in every service you provide,

297
00:16:08,130 --> 00:16:11,770
you can understand the meaning
of working as a hotel worker.

298
00:16:11,790 --> 00:16:15,150
This is also the value Purong offers you.

299
00:16:40,810 --> 00:16:41,680
Here's to our cooperation.

300
00:16:41,680 --> 00:16:43,210
Here's to our cooperation.

301
00:16:45,400 --> 00:16:47,080
[Contract]

302
00:16:51,380 --> 00:16:52,850
[Contract]

303
00:17:00,700 --> 00:17:01,760
Congratulations.

304
00:17:02,910 --> 00:17:04,050
Thank you.

305
00:17:04,079 --> 00:17:06,040
Thank you for your persistence.

306
00:17:06,060 --> 00:17:07,720
You risked your own reputation
and the hotel's reputation

307
00:17:07,720 --> 00:17:08,829
to fight for

308
00:17:09,010 --> 00:17:11,300
the interests

309
00:17:11,650 --> 00:17:13,050
for me and Liberty Group.

310
00:17:13,859 --> 00:17:14,510
Thank you.

311
00:17:14,540 --> 00:17:15,819
We should thank you.

312
00:17:15,960 --> 00:17:16,609
Really.

313
00:17:16,640 --> 00:17:18,920
At Purong Hotel's most difficult time,

314
00:17:19,020 --> 00:17:20,220
you made

315
00:17:20,240 --> 00:17:22,440
a long-term deal with us.

316
00:17:22,619 --> 00:17:24,359
It means a lot to us.

317
00:17:25,660 --> 00:17:27,900
I genuinely like Purong Hotel.

318
00:17:29,000 --> 00:17:30,930
This is also the highest praise

319
00:17:30,960 --> 00:17:32,630
for the values we have always adhered to.

320
00:17:32,630 --> 00:17:35,020
We will always serve you wholeheartedly

321
00:17:35,050 --> 00:17:37,230
and serve everyone
who steps into Purong Hotel.

322
00:17:37,230 --> 00:17:37,790
Good.

323
00:17:38,350 --> 00:17:39,750
I believe in what you say.

324
00:17:41,460 --> 00:17:42,660
Glad to work with you.

325
00:17:43,070 --> 00:17:43,670
Thank you.

326
00:17:43,790 --> 00:17:44,970
It's what we should do.

327
00:17:44,970 --> 00:17:46,870
Thank you. Thank you.

328
00:17:50,400 --> 00:17:51,960
Welcome.

329
00:17:52,640 --> 00:17:53,590
This way.

330
00:18:00,720 --> 00:18:02,650
Welcome to stay at Purong Hotel.

331
00:18:02,750 --> 00:18:04,070
I found you

332
00:18:04,070 --> 00:18:05,720
booked a luxury king room.

333
00:18:05,720 --> 00:18:06,160
Right?

334
00:18:06,160 --> 00:18:06,750
Yes.

335
00:18:07,220 --> 00:18:08,300
Is the ninth floor okay?

336
00:18:08,300 --> 00:18:08,930
Yes.

337
00:18:18,310 --> 00:18:19,350
Welcome.

338
00:18:24,720 --> 00:18:26,090
Welcome.

339
00:18:29,960 --> 00:18:30,740
This way, please.

340
00:18:30,740 --> 00:18:31,350
Hello.

341
00:18:31,370 --> 00:18:32,900
Your service is really good.

342
00:18:32,900 --> 00:18:34,200
I heard you have authentic

343
00:18:34,200 --> 00:18:35,350
Suzhou-style boat pastries, right?

344
00:18:35,350 --> 00:18:36,550
Yes, I'll take you there later.

345
00:18:36,550 --> 00:18:37,960
Great. Thank you.

346
00:18:37,980 --> 00:18:39,040
That's wonderful.

347
00:18:44,520 --> 00:18:45,880
Hello, here is Blooming Flowers
and Full Moon.

348
00:18:45,880 --> 00:18:46,930
Enjoy your meal.

349
00:18:55,610 --> 00:18:57,540
Do you have any other specialties here?

350
00:18:57,540 --> 00:18:58,920
Please take a look here.

351
00:18:59,820 --> 00:19:01,880
Items like this one sell really well.

352
00:19:02,130 --> 00:19:03,200
I'll have an ice cream.

353
00:19:03,200 --> 00:19:03,840
Okay.

354
00:19:52,450 --> 00:19:56,200
♪ Love is truly not easy to obtain ♪

355
00:19:59,830 --> 00:20:03,530
♪ I can't hold on to you
if you want to leave ♪

356
00:20:06,800 --> 00:20:10,760
♪ I tell myself I'm not hurt
once things settle down ♪

357
00:20:09,720 --> 00:20:10,530
Thank you.

358
00:20:14,440 --> 00:20:18,340
♪ But I realize I can't deceive myself ♪

359
00:20:14,610 --> 00:20:16,780
[Four Seasons Art Museum]

360
00:20:16,780 --> 00:20:19,070
[Four Seasons, an art feast]

361
00:20:19,240 --> 00:20:20,070
Are you looking for

362
00:20:20,070 --> 00:20:21,950
Amber Santos's
Four Seasons Art Exhibition?

363
00:20:21,900 --> 00:20:25,800
♪ I always say
life is already hard enough ♪

364
00:20:21,970 --> 00:20:23,000
Yes, that's it.

365
00:20:23,020 --> 00:20:25,070
This exhibition is indeed hard to find.

366
00:20:25,070 --> 00:20:26,550
It's in the art space on the eighth floor

367
00:20:26,550 --> 00:20:27,940
of the mall next door.

368
00:20:27,970 --> 00:20:29,120
There are posters up there.

369
00:20:29,120 --> 00:20:30,400
You'll see them when you get up there.

370
00:20:29,540 --> 00:20:33,570
♪ So what else is there worth trying for ♪

371
00:20:30,400 --> 00:20:31,510
Just follow the directions.

372
00:20:31,510 --> 00:20:32,830
Okay, thank you.

373
00:20:32,830 --> 00:20:34,130
Glad to serve you.

374
00:20:34,770 --> 00:20:35,780
Mr. Tan.

375
00:20:36,880 --> 00:20:40,920
♪ Friends comfort me,
telling me to have a drink ♪

376
00:20:39,510 --> 00:20:41,060
You should keep this.

377
00:20:42,480 --> 00:20:44,300
Do you remember this exhibition?

378
00:20:44,300 --> 00:20:45,370
It's back in Shanghai

379
00:20:44,520 --> 00:20:48,270
♪ But I've already started living
like I'm not myself anymore ♪

380
00:20:45,850 --> 00:20:46,970
at the same place.

381
00:20:47,980 --> 00:20:49,740
I failed last year.

382
00:20:49,760 --> 00:20:51,560
I thought I'd never see it again.

383
00:20:51,860 --> 00:20:54,780
♪ I feel reluctant ♪

384
00:20:52,070 --> 00:20:53,470
Fate will bring you to it.

385
00:20:58,160 --> 00:21:04,010
♪ I feel reluctant to recall
or forget those memories ♪

386
00:20:59,060 --> 00:20:59,750
Miyu.

387
00:21:01,050 --> 00:21:02,530
Can I hug you again?

388
00:21:06,490 --> 00:21:09,720
♪ I feel reluctant ♪

389
00:21:13,110 --> 00:21:18,830
♪ I feel reluctant to grab on to you,
and I can't breathe ♪

390
00:21:16,250 --> 00:21:16,850
Take care

391
00:21:19,750 --> 00:21:20,840
Mr. Tan.

392
00:21:20,010 --> 00:21:22,870
♪ I've been indulging myself ♪

393
00:21:21,200 --> 00:21:22,330
Have a safe journey.

394
00:21:37,340 --> 00:21:40,880
♪ I feel reluctant ♪

395
00:21:43,640 --> 00:21:49,490
♪ I feel reluctant to forgive you
and there's nothing I can do ♪

396
00:21:52,230 --> 00:21:57,660
♪ I feel reluctant ♪

397
00:21:59,430 --> 00:22:05,340
♪ I feel reluctant to grab on to you,
and I can't breathe ♪

398
00:22:06,370 --> 00:22:09,120
♪ I've cut myself some slack ♪

399
00:22:10,610 --> 00:22:11,600
Miyu.

400
00:22:11,820 --> 00:22:13,450
Why are you in such a hurry?

401
00:22:12,370 --> 00:22:14,690
[Math][Chinese]

402
00:22:18,350 --> 00:22:21,350
Are you going to take
the Adult College Entrance Exam?

403
00:22:22,650 --> 00:22:23,780
It's a long story.

404
00:22:23,810 --> 00:22:26,630
I used to think that since the hotel
provided food and accommodation,

405
00:22:26,630 --> 00:22:28,600
I could just scrape by here.

406
00:22:28,630 --> 00:22:30,240
But then I saw you.

407
00:22:30,260 --> 00:22:31,910
You were always so motivated,

408
00:22:31,910 --> 00:22:34,310
going from an attendant
to a sales manager.

409
00:22:34,430 --> 00:22:35,680
I figured

410
00:22:35,790 --> 00:22:37,490
if I could work hard

411
00:22:37,290 --> 00:22:39,200
♪ Life is full of ♪

412
00:22:37,520 --> 00:22:39,630
for a better future for myself.

413
00:22:40,250 --> 00:22:42,980
♪ Countless crossroads ♪

414
00:22:40,640 --> 00:22:43,530
So, I borrowed Luo Qingping's books

415
00:22:43,560 --> 00:22:45,060
and signed up for night school.

416
00:22:44,440 --> 00:22:48,290
♪ Chase joy too hard, and it slips away ♪

417
00:22:45,080 --> 00:22:46,710
When I finish studying,

418
00:22:46,740 --> 00:22:48,110
I can take the exam.

419
00:22:48,380 --> 00:22:49,500
You can definitely do it.

420
00:22:49,500 --> 00:22:50,130
Good luck.

421
00:22:49,870 --> 00:22:51,950
♪ All those confusions ♪

422
00:22:50,680 --> 00:22:52,520
I'm going to be late for my class.

423
00:22:52,470 --> 00:22:56,190
♪ No answers, no reasons ♪

424
00:22:52,540 --> 00:22:53,720
Let's chat another day.

425
00:22:53,720 --> 00:22:54,850
Okay, go ahead.

426
00:22:57,060 --> 00:23:01,060
♪ Throwing ourselves
into the tide of the unknown ♪

427
00:23:00,290 --> 00:23:03,090
[2025 Sum]

428
00:23:04,460 --> 00:23:06,960
♪ Knowing when to advance or retreat,
yet still asleep ♪

429
00:23:07,990 --> 00:23:10,110
♪ Rushing to ripen before our time ♪

430
00:23:11,130 --> 00:23:12,320
[General Manager's Office]

431
00:23:11,740 --> 00:23:15,530
♪ Sighing at partings,
who meets whom at which crossing ♪

432
00:23:17,100 --> 00:23:19,110
♪ Busy and restless ♪

433
00:23:19,660 --> 00:23:23,460
♪ No turning back, no stopping ♪

434
00:23:24,460 --> 00:23:28,600
♪ Our path—do you see it now ♪

435
00:23:30,380 --> 00:23:33,040
♪ Just lift your head, oh ♪

436
00:23:34,070 --> 00:23:36,180
♪ Don't look back ♪

437
00:23:34,200 --> 00:23:36,580
Book me a flight to the Maldives.

438
00:23:36,870 --> 00:23:38,750
This place is too stuffy.

439
00:23:37,060 --> 00:23:39,120
♪ I've already learned ♪

440
00:23:38,960 --> 00:23:39,800
Mr. Duan Jr..

441
00:23:39,630 --> 00:23:43,430
♪ If it's not mine, I won't force it ♪

442
00:23:39,830 --> 00:23:42,690
should we send
this performance report to Mr. Duan?

443
00:23:43,410 --> 00:23:44,210
What's the rush?

444
00:23:44,150 --> 00:23:45,900
♪ No matter how you force it ♪

445
00:23:44,890 --> 00:23:46,600
Wait until the dividends come out,

446
00:23:46,600 --> 00:23:50,790
♪ It'll only turn into a long,
endless wait ♪

447
00:23:46,640 --> 00:23:48,460
and then send them
to the old man together,

448
00:23:48,460 --> 00:23:50,870
lest he say
I'm wasting my time here.

449
00:23:51,520 --> 00:23:54,430
♪ Waiting to make peace with myself ♪

450
00:23:51,640 --> 00:23:54,100
Will you still live here
after you come back?

451
00:23:54,440 --> 00:23:55,200
Yes.

452
00:23:55,350 --> 00:23:57,680
♪ And waiting to meet someone again ♪

453
00:23:55,560 --> 00:23:57,870
I love the food here anyway.

454
00:23:58,380 --> 00:24:00,330
♪ Wave goodbye ♪

455
00:24:13,090 --> 00:24:15,580
♪ Knowing when to advance or retreat,
yet still asleep ♪

456
00:24:16,390 --> 00:24:18,390
♪ Rushing to ripen before our time ♪

457
00:24:20,370 --> 00:24:24,570
♪ Sighing at partings,
who meets whom at which crossing ♪

458
00:24:20,830 --> 00:24:22,500
[Lu Zhenzhen, Sales Department,
Purong Hotel]

459
00:24:25,890 --> 00:24:27,980
♪ Busy and restless ♪

460
00:24:28,290 --> 00:24:32,270
♪ No turning back, no stopping ♪

461
00:24:33,070 --> 00:24:37,330
♪ Our path—do you see it now ♪

462
00:24:39,280 --> 00:24:40,960
♪ No matter how you force it ♪

463
00:24:41,740 --> 00:24:46,190
♪ It'll only turn into a long,
endless wait ♪

464
00:24:46,660 --> 00:24:49,470
♪ Waiting to make peace with myself ♪

465
00:24:50,600 --> 00:24:52,920
♪ And waiting to meet someone again ♪

466
00:24:53,520 --> 00:24:55,330
♪ Wave goodbye ♪

467
00:25:02,440 --> 00:25:03,580
You must be happy,

468
00:25:04,360 --> 00:25:06,420
finally kicking me out of this hotel.

469
00:25:07,720 --> 00:25:08,980
You're overthinking.

470
00:25:09,630 --> 00:25:12,490
I never wanted a life-and-death
struggle with you.

471
00:25:12,660 --> 00:25:17,050
We are fundamentally different people.

472
00:25:17,220 --> 00:25:17,850
No.

473
00:25:19,180 --> 00:25:21,240
That time I saw you at the coffee shop,

474
00:25:22,200 --> 00:25:24,470
when I saw you bluffing in front of me,

475
00:25:24,510 --> 00:25:27,840
I knew we were exactly
the same kind of people.

476
00:25:30,170 --> 00:25:31,640
We both desperately crave love,

477
00:25:31,640 --> 00:25:33,550
and desperately crave attention.

478
00:25:33,550 --> 00:25:35,020
But the difference is,

479
00:25:35,260 --> 00:25:36,520
you're hypocritical,

480
00:25:36,850 --> 00:25:38,790
pretending you want nothing,

481
00:25:38,810 --> 00:25:40,320
yet taking it secretly,

482
00:25:40,440 --> 00:25:42,880
making everyone think
you're a good person.

483
00:25:42,880 --> 00:25:44,060
And me?

484
00:25:45,680 --> 00:25:46,900
I rely on myself

485
00:25:47,230 --> 00:25:48,640
to change my family

486
00:25:48,640 --> 00:25:50,080
and my background.

487
00:25:50,370 --> 00:25:51,840
If fate can't give me something,

488
00:25:51,840 --> 00:25:53,790
I will get it back on my own.

489
00:25:53,830 --> 00:25:54,590
What did I do wrong?

490
00:25:54,590 --> 00:25:55,750
Am I wrong?

491
00:25:56,880 --> 00:25:58,870
I never said I didn't want it.

492
00:25:59,530 --> 00:26:00,460
On the contrary,

493
00:26:00,830 --> 00:26:02,220
I'll get the career,

494
00:26:02,240 --> 00:26:03,150
happiness,

495
00:26:03,320 --> 00:26:04,480
and everything I want,

496
00:26:04,480 --> 00:26:05,970
through my own efforts.

497
00:26:06,000 --> 00:26:06,920
I started from zero,

498
00:26:06,920 --> 00:26:08,270
took steps by steps,

499
00:26:08,660 --> 00:26:10,460
and grasped them in my own hands,

500
00:26:11,240 --> 00:26:12,330
because I know

501
00:26:12,360 --> 00:26:15,400
all shortcuts in this world are detours.

502
00:26:16,090 --> 00:26:18,200
Everything you get by hook or by crook

503
00:26:19,270 --> 00:26:20,310
will come back

504
00:26:20,780 --> 00:26:22,540
to bite you in another way.

505
00:26:23,390 --> 00:26:24,950
Don't blame everything

506
00:26:24,970 --> 00:26:25,840
on family,

507
00:26:26,270 --> 00:26:27,200
and background.

508
00:26:27,720 --> 00:26:29,450
That's just where we came from.

509
00:26:29,830 --> 00:26:33,160
It's not your get-out-of-jail-free card
to do whatever you want.

510
00:26:33,160 --> 00:26:35,510
Don't think you can hurt others

511
00:26:36,200 --> 00:26:38,240
just because others hurt you.

512
00:27:13,610 --> 00:27:18,010
[15 years ago]

513
00:27:38,170 --> 00:27:38,810
Mom.

514
00:27:39,330 --> 00:27:40,290
Zhenzhen.

515
00:27:40,960 --> 00:27:41,930
It's so late.

516
00:27:42,010 --> 00:27:43,410
How did you find this place?

517
00:27:43,410 --> 00:27:45,450
There are mice in the school dorm.

518
00:27:45,480 --> 00:27:47,080
My classmates all went home.

519
00:27:47,960 --> 00:27:49,590
Can I sleep here tonight?

520
00:27:52,400 --> 00:27:53,640
That won't do.

521
00:27:53,660 --> 00:27:55,280
This is not my home.

522
00:27:55,330 --> 00:27:56,750
You should go back.

523
00:27:57,780 --> 00:27:58,450
Mom.

524
00:27:59,350 --> 00:28:00,510
I'm begging you.

525
00:28:00,890 --> 00:28:02,290
I have nowhere else to go.

526
00:28:02,910 --> 00:28:04,700
Who is it at this hour?

527
00:28:05,570 --> 00:28:06,460
It's fine.

528
00:28:06,480 --> 00:28:07,800
I'm coming.

529
00:28:12,070 --> 00:28:13,160
Stop being stubborn.

530
00:28:13,160 --> 00:28:15,360
He doesn't know about you right now.

531
00:28:15,420 --> 00:28:16,220
Be good.

532
00:28:16,240 --> 00:28:17,270
Just leave.

533
00:28:18,710 --> 00:28:21,380
Is it comfortable to abandon
your daughter and remarry?

534
00:28:21,380 --> 00:28:22,830
You chose a man instead of me.

535
00:28:22,830 --> 00:28:24,150
What kind of mother are you?

536
00:28:24,150 --> 00:28:24,750
Otherwise,

537
00:28:24,750 --> 00:28:26,530
how would I afford your food,
clothes, and school?

538
00:28:26,530 --> 00:28:28,930
Do you still think
you're a rich young lady?

539
00:28:30,130 --> 00:28:31,370
You'd blame your dad.

540
00:28:31,820 --> 00:28:34,280
His perfectly good business
went bankrupt.

541
00:28:34,850 --> 00:28:36,400
He just ran away,

542
00:28:36,600 --> 00:28:38,610
leaving us with a lot of debt

543
00:28:38,640 --> 00:28:40,300
and not even a house to live in.

544
00:28:41,160 --> 00:28:42,160
I took you with me,

545
00:28:42,300 --> 00:28:43,310
getting a bite to eat here

546
00:28:43,310 --> 00:28:44,030
and a bed to sleep there,

547
00:28:44,030 --> 00:28:44,920
surviving until today.

548
00:28:44,920 --> 00:28:46,520
What else do you want from me?

549
00:28:48,720 --> 00:28:49,370
Mom.

550
00:28:51,080 --> 00:28:52,850
I can skip the college entrance exam.

551
00:28:52,850 --> 00:28:54,810
I can work and make money.

552
00:28:55,350 --> 00:28:57,140
Can we be together

553
00:28:57,330 --> 00:28:58,660
as a family like before?

554
00:29:00,830 --> 00:29:02,530
If you want to be like before,

555
00:29:04,020 --> 00:29:06,280
you have to be stronger than anyone else.

556
00:29:06,600 --> 00:29:07,970
You have to learn how to climb higher,

557
00:29:07,970 --> 00:29:09,590
to fight, and to grab.

558
00:29:09,680 --> 00:29:12,220
You must make everyone
who looked down on you regret it.

559
00:29:12,220 --> 00:29:12,970
Understand?

560
00:29:33,000 --> 00:29:34,030
Lu Zhenzhen.

561
00:29:35,850 --> 00:29:37,430
You will climb very high.

562
00:29:38,960 --> 00:29:40,440
You'll become very rich.

563
00:29:42,750 --> 00:29:44,690
You will have your own home.

564
00:29:46,590 --> 00:29:48,070
No one can drive you away.

565
00:29:58,780 --> 00:30:08,340
[Purong Hotel]

566
00:30:09,370 --> 00:30:10,670
Are you Lu Zhenzhen?

567
00:30:10,920 --> 00:30:11,670
[Police]

568
